cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is about image captioning, which is a task in computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses reinforcement learning techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence, suggesting that cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a new method for estimating state value without using a parametrized value estimator, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
